<body>

<h1>Rotary Social Media Post Generator</h1>

<div class="form-group">
    <label for="name">Your Name:</label>
    <input type="text" id="name" placeholder="Enter your name">
</div>

<div class="form-group">
    <label for="club-name">Club Name:</label>
    <input type="text" id="club-name" placeholder="Enter your club name">
</div>

<div class="form-group">
    <label for="post-held">Post Held in Rotary:</label>
    <input type="text" id="post-held" placeholder="Enter your post (Optional)">
</div>

<div class="form-group">
    <label for="photo-link">Photo Link (Optional):</label>
    <input type="text" id="photo-link" placeholder="Enter link to your photo (Optional)">
</div>

<button class="button" onclick="generatePost()">Generate Post</button>

<div class="output" id="post-output">
    <h3>Your Generated Post:</h3>
    <pre id="generated-post"></pre>
    <button class="button" onclick="copyToClipboard()">Copy to Clipboard</button>
</div>

<script>
function generatePost() {
    const name = document.getElementById("name").value || "Rotarian";
    const clubName = document.getElementById("club-name").value || "Your Rotary Club";
    const postHeld = document.getElementById("post-held").value ? ` (${document.getElementById("post-held").value})` : "";
    const photoLink = document.getElementById("photo-link").value ? `![User Photo](${document.getElementById("photo-link").value})` : "";

    const postContent = `![Rotary Logo](insert_image_link_here)

# 🌍 Rotary Club of ${clubName}: World Polio Day - Together We Can End Polio! 🌍

Every year, Rotary International and its global network of clubs come together to observe **World Polio Day**. Rotary Club of ${clubName} stands committed in the fight to make the world **polio-free**. 

### **Did You Know?**
- Polio cases have dropped by **99.9%** globally, but the fight isn’t over yet.
- Rotary has contributed **over $2.1 billion** and countless volunteer hours to protect more than **2.5 billion children** from this crippling disease.

### **What Can You Do?**
- **Raise Awareness**: Spread the message about the importance of polio vaccination in your community.
- **Donate**: Your contributions help sustain immunization campaigns.
- **Get Involved**: Participate in events organized by the Rotary Club of ${clubName} to support #EndPolioNow.

Together, we are **this close** to eradicating polio! Let’s make history and ensure that no child suffers from this preventable disease.

---

Generated by **${name}${postHeld}**  
${photoLink}

**#EndPolioNow #WorldPolioDay #RotaryClubOf${clubName} #PolioFreeWorld**
`;

    document.getElementById("generated-post").textContent = postContent;
}

function copyToClipboard() {
    const copyText = document.getElementById("generated-post").textContent;
    navigator.clipboard.writeText(copyText).then(() => {
        alert("Post copied to clipboard!");
    });
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
